properties.sfomuseum:description: Set of color postcards depicting photographic images of Czechoslovak Airlines fleet and operations.a. envelope/folder;b. color postcard depicting photographic image of Czechoslovak Airlines aircraft parked on tarmac with passengers boarding;c. color postcard depicting photographic image of Czechoslovak Airlines Ilyushin Il-62 parked on tarmac; three-quarter rear view; Bratislava Airport;d. color postcard depicting photographic image of interior of unidentified airport terminal; elevated view; Czechoslovak Airlines counter visible in lower left corner;e. color postcard depicting photographic image of Czechoslovak Airlines Tupolev Tu-134 parked on tarmac; three-quarter frontal view, person standing in foreground;f. color postcard depicting photographic image of Czechoslovak Airlines aerial view of Prague Ruzyne International Airport; airside view; aircraft parked on tarmac near airport buildings; postcard issued by Czechoslovak Airlines;g. color postcard depicting photographic image of interior of restaurant or cafe ;h. color postcard depicting photographic image of Czechoslovak Airlines / Československé Aerolinie aircraft parked on tarmac; profile view;i. color postcard depicting photographic image of Československé Aerolinie aircraft parked on tarmac; profile view;j. color postcard depicting photographic image of Czechoslovak Airlines interior of hangar with tail sections of two Czechoslovak Airlines aircraft visible; maintenance equipment and workers in foreground;k. color postcard depicting photographic image of Czechoslovak Airlines aircraft; detail view of rear cargo door and engines; two baggage handlers loading cargo with forklift.
properties.wof:name: postcard set: Czechoslovak Airlines
